                    <span>I guess the positive reviews come from Cold Fusion developers.  I'm trying to use Access or SQL, and none of the examples worked for me.  I noticed a bug as well.  None of my correspondence to the author was answered, and there is no list of errata on his web page.  The book was a waste of $50 for a project I needed done yesterday.</span>
                  
              
